text: RTV Kozarska Dubica or РТВ КД is a local Bosnian public cable television channel based in Kozarska Dubica municipality. Program is mainly produced in Serbian language. Dub Radio is also part of public municipality services. == References == == External links == * Official website of RTV Kozarska Dubica * Website of CRA BiH Category:Television stations in Bosnia and Herzegovina
